\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $CombineLatest$
\end_inset

: Creates a new stream from two existing streams.
 Whenever a new item is received in either of the streams, 
\begin_inset Formula $CombineLatest$
\end_inset

