 For reactive instance variables 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 in the JavaScript-based rivarjs, the expression 
\begin_inset Formula $lift((x,y)=>x*y,X,Y)$
\end_inset

